Title: Patent Pending: Play Madison Square Garden
Overview:
Patent Pending has been so hard as an amazing band for 13 years! Let's try to get people who love what they're doing on the radio and play big venues instead of the ones who do it for the money! Sign this petition so we can get Patent Pending to play at Madison Square Garden before 2014 ends.

(btw: at the bottom it's supposed to say "To: Madison Square Garden" not "To: Patent Pending")
Letter Body: Have Patent Pending Play Madison Square Garden
